Golden Bay Cruise
Aug 2016 ‚Ä¢ Friends
Booked this cruise I'm Hanoi with Golden Bay cruises for 3 days and 2 nights. All went to plan when we arrived on the boat in Halong. The boat was comfortable and the staff were friendly. After our first night we were transferred to Cat Ba island. Although not the most amazing island we had a pleasant enough time. Day 3 things changed unfortunately we had to evacuated from the island due to a typhoon hitting the area. At first slightly suspicious we weren't sure if this was a scam. However on arrival at the ferry terminal we clocked the number of locals leaving as well it seemed legit. Quite annoyed we had missed out on quite a large portion of our $119 tour we went back to our travel agent Tony. He was aware of the issue and refunded is a portion of our money. Hence the full stars rating.
